Logical Definition (CLD)

This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Include codes fromhttp://snomed.info/sct version 📍 where concept is-a 404684003 (Clinical finding)
  • Include codes fromhttp://snomed.info/sct version 📍 where concept is-a 272379006 (Event)
  • Include codes fromhttp://snomed.info/sct version 📍 where concept is-a 243796009 (Situation with explicit context)
